quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  10,62,"Nimutegere neza mwebwe bakunzi b’Imana, ntimuzoba mufise ubwobwa canke ntimuzoba mufise agahinda"
  10,63,Nabo nibamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri bakaba bayigamburukira
  10,64,"Barafise ibikorwa vyiza mubuzima bwo ng’aha kw’isi no k’umusi w’imperuka, rero ntibahindagurika mumajambo y’Imana, uko rero niko gutsinda gukuru"
  10,65,"Kandi ntuterwe n’agahinda kubera amajambo yabo, mu vy’ukuri iteka ryose niry’Imana, niyo yumva kandi niyo ifise ubumenyi buhagije"
  10,66,"Nimwumvirize, ntankeka ibiri mw’Ijuru hamwe n’ibiri kw’Isi vyose nivy’Imana, na bamwe basenga ibitari Imana, ntibakurikira abo babagereranya atari ivyikeko gusa, kandi ntibavuga atari ububeshi gusa"
  10,67,"Niyo yabagiriye ijoro kugira ngo muruhukire mwo, n’umutaga w’umuco, mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo ibimenyetso ku bantu bumva"
  10,68,"Bavuga yuko Imana yigiriye ikibondo, nayo ikaba iri kure yivyo, kandi irikwijije, ibintu vyose ni rwiwe ibiri mumajuru n’ibiri kw’Isi, namwe ntavyemezo mufise kuri ivyo, mbega mwivugira gusa hejuru y’Imana kuvyo mutazi"
  10,69,"Vuga uti:- bamwe badukana ububeshi ku Mana y’ukuri abo ntatsinzi bafise"
  10,70,"N’amahirwe makeyi cane kuri iy’Isi, hanyuma iwacu niho hari ingaruka yabo, aho niho tuzoba honjesha ibihano bikaze kubera bwabuhakanyi bwabo"